title: Goldie Lookin Chain COMPLETE COLECTION (2001 - 2008)
description:
This torrent is my huge collection of Goldie Lookin Chain songs.

If you did not know already, Goldie Lookin Chain (Or GLC as they are sometimes known as) are a Welsh comic-rap band
who have become very popular with underground collectors due to the elusivity of their tracks.


It is Comprised of all of their Label releases and CD-R albums that they sold themselves before they were signed. 
A lot of this material is very rare.
It also has All of their Podcasts to date, and remixes that I have collected over the years.
I know that there is some material missing, material that is VERY rare. i have listed all of the
tracks that I do not have in the "...Then Read This" File that is attached to this torrent.

After downloading this torrent, you can always go to www.glcforum.com and sign up and show off your collection!
